    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "wait antibiotic ointment is otc? i didnt think i could buy those without a prescription. is there a specific brand u recommend that i can just grab at the pharmacy? and like, how many times a day should i be putting it in? i really dont want to go to the doctor if i can just fix it myself tonight.",
